        </div>
        <div class="panel-body" style="font-size: larger">
          <ul class="custom-bullet">
            <li>Continue onboarding arts organizations into Artsdata.ca </li>
            <li>Improve data quality </li>
            <li>Expand use of data sources including databases, websites and other open data sources </li>
            <li>Develop applications that enable human interaction with Artsdata </li>
            <li>Support applications and services that consume data from Artsdata.ca </li>
            <li>Synchronize global identifiers between Artsdata.ca and Wikidata.org to interlink data about places,
